            "title": "日股收升342點，一周累計挫逾半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日股低開高走，日經指數重上55000點，收市報55620點，升342點，升幅0.62%，連升兩日。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">不過，日股本周累計仍急挫約5.5%，扭轉上星期升勢。</p>\n</div>",
