            "title": "台股低收0.2%　本周累跌逾半成",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">台灣股市反覆低收，加權指數收市報33599點，跌73點，跌幅0.22%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">指數本周累計下跌逾5.1%。</p>\n</div>",
